			博客






	
		
			
个人简介
			
			<spanstyle="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;
mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:
minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">解利军，男，1980<spanstyle="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:
Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:
minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">年生，浙江大学副教授。2002<spanstyle="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:
Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:
minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">年6<spanstyle="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:
Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:
minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">月获浙江大学热能动力工程学士学位，2007<spanstyle="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:
Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:
minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">年6<spanstyle="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:
Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:
minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">月获浙江大学计算机科学与技术专业博士学位，2007<spanstyle="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:
Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:
minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">年7<spanstyle="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:
Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:
minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">月起至今在浙江大学任教。期间2011.4<spanstyle="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:
Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:
minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">月-2011.8<spanstyle="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:
Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:
minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">月在TexasA&amp;MUniversity<spanstyle="font-family:宋体;
mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:
宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;
mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">应用数学系访学。
<spanstyle="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;
mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:
Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">&nbsp;&nbsp;主要研究方向数值模拟支撑技术研究，重点是前后处理技术，属于计算机科学和计算力学的交叉领域。具体研究内容包括科学数据分析和可视化，并行计算和计算机辅助工程。先后获得2<spanstyle="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:
Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:
minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">项自然科学基金项目面上项目资助（2009-2012<spanstyle="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:
Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:
minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">，2013-2016<spanstyle="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:
Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:
minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">）<spanstyle="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:
Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:
minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">、1<spanstyle="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:
Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:
minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">项浙江省自然科学基金项目资助（2012-2013）、1项浙江省科技厅项目资助（2009-2010）、1项中国博后基金项目资助（2008-2009），以及多项重大项目子项目。共发表论文40余篇，申请发明专利5项（已授权2项），软件著作权4项。
<spanstyle="font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:
minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;TimesNewRoman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:
宋体">代表性成果：
<spanstyle="font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:
宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;TimesNewRoman&quot;;
mso-bidi-font-family:宋体">（1）设计和实现了高端数字样机系统HEDP的软件架构和主要的后处理技术，该系统是我国有特色的自主知识产权CAE软件。研发了大规模非定常数据的智能分析方法，将一系列人工智能和数据挖掘算法改进后应用于科学数据分析。相关成果得到了具体工程应用。
<spanstyle="font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:
宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;TimesNewRoman&quot;;
mso-bidi-font-family:宋体">（2）研发了一种自适应于任意表面、可伸缩、可无缝拼接的智能投影系统。基于计算机视觉和并行可视化方法，大幅度降低了绘制和显示系统的构建、维护和使用复杂度，能低成本、高效率地实现大规模科学数据的高精度、沉浸式分析。<spanstyle="font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:
宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;TimesNewRoman&quot;;
mso-bidi-font-family:宋体">
			
				
			工作研究领域
			
			科学数据可视分析，并行计算，图形图像，计算机视觉
			
				
